  78:middlewares/freertos/source/event_groups.c **** /*
  79:middlewares/freertos/source/event_groups.c ****  * Test the bits set in uxCurrentEventBits to see if the wait condition is met.
  80:middlewares/freertos/source/event_groups.c ****  * The wait condition is defined by xWaitForAllBits.  If xWaitForAllBits is
  81:middlewares/freertos/source/event_groups.c ****  * pdTRUE then the wait condition is met if all the bits set in uxBitsToWaitFor
  82:middlewares/freertos/source/event_groups.c ****  * are also set in uxCurrentEventBits.  If xWaitForAllBits is pdFALSE then the
  83:middlewares/freertos/source/event_groups.c ****  * wait condition is met if any of the bits set in uxBitsToWait for are also set
  84:middlewares/freertos/source/event_groups.c ****  * in uxCurrentEventBits.
  85:middlewares/freertos/source/event_groups.c ****  */
